Class MemberSuspectEvent

      • org.springframework.geode.distributed.event.MembershipEvent<MemberSuspectEvent>
        • org.springframework.geode.distributed.event.support.MemberSuspectEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class MemberSuspectEvent
extends MembershipEvent<MemberSuspectEvent>
    MembershipEvent fired when a DistributedMember of the DistributedSystem is suspected of being unresponsive to other peer members in the cluster.
    Since:
    1.3.0
    See Also:
    DistributedMember, DistributedSystem, MembershipEvent, Serialized Form
